{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide introduces the most important features of the Apodini Metadata system. It is primarily targeted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"towards users of the Metadata system, but can also be used by Metadata Providers to get an overview"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the Metadata system."}]},{"anchor":"Declaration-Blocks","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Declaration Blocks"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Apodini provides Metadata Declaration Blocks on the following types: "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Component"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/WebService"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Handler"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Content"},{"type":"text","text":" (Note that the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" property for "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Content"},{"type":"text","text":" types is static)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inside those Declaration Blocks you can place any applicable Metadata instance to apply it to the respective element."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Below shows the Metadata Declaration Blocks for all the above-mentioned protocols."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ExampleWebService: WebService {","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        \/\/ ...","    }","}","","struct ExampleComponent: Component {","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        \/\/ ...","    }","}","","struct ExampleHandler: Handler {","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        \/\/ ...","    }","}","","struct ExampleContent: Content {","    \/\/ ...","    static var metadata: Metadata {","        \/\/ ...","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some Metadata Definitions might only be available on a subset of the above Metadata Declaration Blocks."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Looking at the example of the predefined "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/HandlerDescriptionMetadata"},{"type":"text","text":" Metadata which can be used in all the above Metadata Declaration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Blocks, to add a textual description to the respective component. Adding a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/HandlerMetadataNamespace\/Description"},{"type":"text","text":" Metadata to a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Handler"},{"type":"text","text":" could look like the following:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ExampleHandler: Handler {","    func handle() -> String {","        \"Hello World!\"","    }","","    var metadata: Metadata {","        Description(\"This Endpoint serves a message to the world!\")","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Metadata-Blocks","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Metadata Blocks"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Metadata Blocks are a way of grouping your Metadata Declaration such that it may improve code readability or introduce"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"any user defined semantics to the reader. Metadata Blocks are functionally not different to Metadata Declarations made"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"without Metadata Blocks."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The special "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Block"},{"type":"text","text":" Metadata is available in all the above Metadata Declaration Blocks."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It may be used as follows:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ExampleHandler: Handler {","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        \/\/ ...","        Block {","            Description(\"This Endpoint serves a message to the world!\")","        }","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Reusable-Metadata-Blocks","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Reusable Metadata Blocks"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In some situations it might make sense to create Metadata Declarations which are independent of the component(s)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"where they are used. Reasons may be to declutter the Metadata Declaration of your component or to reuse certain"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Metadata on several components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Apodini provides Reusable Metadata Blocks for such circumstances. There are the following protocols available,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"depending on where you want to apply your Metadata Block:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/HandlerMetadataBlock"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/WebServiceMetadataBlock"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/ComponentMetadataBlock"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ContentMetadataBlock"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An example "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HandlerMetadataBlock"},{"type":"text","text":" might look like the following:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ReusableExampleMetadata: HandlerMetadataBlock {","    var metadata: Metadata {","        \/\/ ...","    }","}","","struct ExampleHandler: Handler {","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        ReusableExampleMetadata()","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Restricted-Metadata-Blocks","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Restricted Metadata Blocks"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Chapter "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Metadata Blocks"},{"type":"text","text":" introduced the general purpose Metadata Block "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Block"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Metadata Providers might choose to provide custom named Metadata Blocks which are restricted to only contain"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"certain types of Metadata."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You might imagine a Restricted Metadata Block called "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Descriptions"},{"type":"text","text":" which is restricted to only contain"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/HandlerDescriptionMetadata"},{"type":"text","text":" Metadata (and may also contain nested "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Descriptions"},{"type":"text","text":" Blocks)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such a Block may be used like the following:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ExampleHandler: Handler {","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        \/\/ ...","        Descriptions {","            Description(\"This is a Example Handler!\")","        }","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Component-and-Handler-Modifiers","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Component and Handler Modifiers"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Apodini offers a range of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Component"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Handler"},{"type":"text","text":" Modifiers which can be used to add additional Metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the respective Component. The following Modifiers are provided:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Component\/metadata(@MetadataBuilder:)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Component\/metadata(_:)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Handler\/metadata(@MetadataBuilder:)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Handler\/metadata(_:)-154i8"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For both "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Component"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Handler"},{"type":"text","text":" there are each two "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" modifiers which can be used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to either add a specific instance of Metadata or add Metadata Declaration Blocks to the respective Component."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Below are two examples demonstrating on how to use each of those Modifiers to add a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Description"},{"type":"text","text":" Metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the Handler in the Component Tree:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ExampleComponent: Component {","    var content: some Component {","        ExampleHandler()","            .metadata(Description(\"Description for the predefined `ExampleHandler`\"))","    }","}","","struct ExampleComponent: Component {","    var content: some Component {","        ExampleHandler()","            .metadata {","                Description(\"Description for the predefined `ExampleHandler`\")","                \/\/ ...","            }","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Conditional-Metadata","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Conditional Metadata"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Metadata DSL allows for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"if"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"if\/else"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"switch"},{"type":"text","text":" control flow statements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This can be used to conditionally construct Metadata depending on arbitrary state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note that Metadata Declaration Blocks are only evaluated once at startup. Therefore, it is sensible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to base the conditions only on state which is fixed after initialization."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ExampleHandler: Handler {","    var experimental: Bool","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        if experimental {","        Description(\"Note: The new experimental version of the Handler introduces breaking changes!\")","        } else {","            Description (\"This Handler serves as a example!\")","        }","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Loops","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Loops"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"With Swift 5.4, the Metadata DSL allows for usage of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"for .. in .."},{"type":"text","text":" loops to construct multiple Metadata Declarations."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct ExampleHandler: Handler {","    \/\/ ...","    var metadata: Metadata {","        for i in 0...10 {","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/apodini\/metadatauserguide"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/MetadataUserGuide","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A guide on how to use the Metadata system from the perspective of a user writing a web service."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Apodini"}],"role":"collectionGroup","title":"Metadata User Guide"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Metadata"]]},"topicSections":[{"title":"Web Service Elements","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Component","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Handler","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/WebService","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Content"]},{"title":"Metadata Blocks","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/ComponentMetadataBlock","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/HandlerMetadataBlock","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/WebServiceMetadataBlock"]},{"title":"Restricted Metadata Blocks","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/RestrictedComponentMetadataBlock","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/RestrictedHandlerMetadataBlock","doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/RestrictedWebServiceMetadataBlock"]},{"title":"Metadata Modifier","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Apodini\/documentation\/Apodini\/Component\/metadata(_:)"]},{"title":"Metadata built into the Apod